   <br>
   <strong>Solution</strong>
   <br>
   <strong>(i)</strong><br>2m (7n + 1) -3n (7n + 1); 7n + 1 is the HCF of 2m and 3n
   <br>
   2m (7n + 1) -3n (7n + 1) = <strong>(2m – 3n) (7n + 1)</strong>
   <br>
   <strong>(ii)</strong><br>10k<sup>3</sup> + 2k (r + 2); 2k is the HCF of 10k<sup>3</sup> and 2k (r + 2)
   <br>
   10k<sup>3</sup> + 2k (r + 2) = 2k(5k<sup>2</sup> + (r + 2))
   <br>
   10k<sup>3</sup> + 2k (r + 2) = <strong>2k(5k<sup>2</sup> + r + 2)</strong>
   <br>
   <strong>(iii)</strong><br>	(2a + b) (5a – 3b) – (2a + b)<sup>2</sup>  ; (2a + b) is the HCF
   <br>
   (2a + b) (5a – 3b) – (2a + b)<sup>2</sup> = (2a + b) ( (5a – 3b) – (2a + b) )
   <br>
   = (2a + b) (5a – 3b – 2a – b)
   <br>
  = (2a + b) (5a – 2a – 3b – b)
  <br>
  (2a + b) (5a – 3b) – (2a + b)<sup>2</sup>  = <strong>(2a + b) (3a – 4b)</strong>  
  <br>  
  <strong>(iv)</strong><br>	(c – 3y) (d + 2) – c + 3y = (c – 3y) (d + 2) –1 (c – 3y); (c – 3y) is the HCF
   <br>
  = (c – 3y) ( (d + 2) – 1 ) 
  <br>
  = (c – 3y ) ( d + 2 – 1)
  <br>
  (c – 3y) (d + 2) – c + 3y = <strong>(c – 3y) (d + 1)</strong>
  <br>
  <br>
